{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_01","textHome":"我只不过是带着照相机拍照的人而已。@我是不会那么简单就成为拍摄对象的哦。@那么，不要在意我，去别的地方就行了。@我拍了很多别人反感的东西，敌人也很多。@在被人当做我的同伴之前，你还是离开比较好，@不过你要是想跟着我的话，就要做好觉悟哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_17","textHome":"要写报道的话就需要证词对吧？@但是也有看了证据也沉默不语的家伙，@这种时候就只能自己取材了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_18","textHome":"我做了很多伤害对方的事，所以敌人很多。@不过，因为我而获得拯救的人也很多。@实际上，也有人在暗中帮助我。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":400}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_19","textHome":"观鸟报势不可挡。@过去或是今后都是如此！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_20","textHome":"这样子，收集证据的计划就完成了。@不要小看我哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_21","textHome":"就算有着无数能够按下快门的机会，@也会由于技术和体力的不足而错失。@我，已经不想体会这样的遗憾了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_22","textHome":"哪里都不存在什么眼不见心不烦。@善恶混杂的现实之中，也一定存在着真相。@如果不能认同这一点，是得不到我的认同的。@就算这只是我的自我满足也好。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_23","textHome":"真相要在一个人的手中持续发酵。@如果不这样的话是不行的。@如果不是一个人来做，真相就会被其他人歪曲。@我考虑过了，所以今后无论发生什么，@我也要一个人战斗。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_24","textHome":"啊哈哈！被我抓到漏洞的话可就要倒霉了哦。@又想来被我揭露隐私了吗？@没问题，今天我也会拍下来的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_25","textHome":"起得挺早啊。@我无论前一天晚上多忙，@也会准备好带去学校的相机。@话说，能帮我拿一下电吹风吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":400}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_26","textHome":"诶？啊，到了中午大家都聚在了墙报前。@我观察了一下，今天还不错嘛。@也没有来撕报纸的家伙。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_02","textHome":"观鸟令认为摄影师就是要一视同仁。@所以在被拍到奇怪的照片之前，@还是推荐你离开比较好。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_27","textHome":"好，器材全都带上了，差不多该行动了。@你不用跟着我。@虽说放学之后就是八卦的宝库，@但也很容易招人怨恨哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_28","textHome":"真是的，到晚上就全是讨厌的八卦……@哈啊，稍微去看看猫咪吧。@“每日一猫”的照片还没有拍好呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_29","textHome":"哈啊……哈啊……@终于甩掉了吗，真是纠缠不休啊……@要是那么在意的话，@一开始就不要做什么亏心事啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_30","textHome":"啊，是魔女的反应……@这么说的话，应该会有魔法少女过来吧。@她勇猛战斗的身姿，我要好好记录下来才行。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_31","textHome":"无尽镜界……虽然听了有关很多这个的话题，@也一直进行着取材，但这里始终是个谜。@甚至没有一个人在这见过魔女……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":300}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_32","textHome":"我哪边都不想参与，只想待在什么地方看着。@也可以和放心大胆地和我干一场哦。@这样我就不用担心没有题材了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_33","textHome":"从学生间的恋爱到教师的丑闻，@交通事故或是魔法少女的战斗，@只要能成为八卦什么都可以。@这就是观鸟报。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_34","textHome":"这张照片很不错对吧？@虽然拍摄猫咪并不是八卦，@但这样照片反而会拍得更漂亮。@而且报道的评价也很好。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_35","textHome":"好痛，比起打人@还不如做些被拍到的时候应该有的行为才对。@比如用钱解决之类的，@估计是很不想被人看到吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_36","textHome":"在思考照片和新闻稿的时候，@只要喝杯黑咖啡，脑子就灵光了。@你要的话我再去煎一杯。@不过我没有砂糖和牛奶。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_03","textHome":"从以前开始我就总是卷入奇怪的事件中啊。"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_37","textHome":"虽然很理解自己的行为是得不到同情的……@但是，自己居住的地方被拿出来作为地域黑，@而且还广为接受，实在是有些难过……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_38","textHome":"啊啊，你说和泉十七夜我知道，@那个人坦坦荡荡地宣扬着大道理，@简直到了恐怖的程度。@她那种自我毁灭的倾向太过了，@我实在接受不来。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_39","textHome":"啊哈哈！你觉得我会有朋友吗？@不过我有一个能敞开心扉聊各种话的人。@不要对外说哦，我怕会把她卷进来。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_40","textHome":"虽然我很讨厌做别人的手下，@但只要能从魔法少女的宿命中解脱出来，@我想那也是没办法的。@宣传就是我唯一的不正常活动。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_41","textHome":"什么！竟然拍到了我，干得不错嘛。@没问题，我的准则就是@被拍到的那一方才是有错的。@那张照片，你就好好留着吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_42","textHome":"接下来，我不会放过快门的机会哦！"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_43","textHome":"一篇不错的报道出炉了。"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_44","textHome":"抓到证据了！这样就没有反驳的余地了吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_45","textHome":"被拍到的那一方才是有错的，记着不吃亏。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_46","textHome":"只要我的活动能够救助他人就够了。"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_04","textHome":"一定要掌握证据，这就是我的信条。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_63","textHome":"就用这一炮把你点燃吧！"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_64","textHome":"拍摄对象被抓住了……"}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_65","textHome":"去吧，不是扩散而是爆散哦——!!"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":400}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_66","textHome":"一枚都不要浪费啊。"}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_05","textHome":"我成为棋子就只有这一刻而已。"}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_13","textHome":"最近的照片景深都很棒。@不过我还要继续积累才行。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600,"motion":300}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_14","textHome":"光圈值和快门速度都没问题！@现在我就能把一切都清楚地拍下来了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_15","textHome":"哈哈，想听我拍照的故事吗？@那我就告诉你吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_16","textHome":"这和事情好坏无关。@只要有成为八卦的机会，我就会立即拍下来。@这就是我的能力。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":400}]}]},"version":3}